name: Account
description:
As a visitor of the ecommerce website
	I want to be able to see and update my account details
	So that my details for ordering and delivery are correct

steps.name: I am not logged in
I am on the log in page
I enter my username
I enter my password
I click the login button
I am on logged in
I am logged in on the site
I click the Log out button
I receive feedback that I am logged out
I cannot visit my account page anymore
I am logged in on the site
I navigate to my orders
I see a list of my orders
I can open an order to see the order details
I am logged in on the site
I navigate to the personal information page
I update my details
I receive feedback that my account is updated
I am logged in on the site
I navigate to the personal information page
I change my street name
I receive feedback that my account is updated

name: Checkout
description:
As a visitor of the ecommerce website
	I want to be able to do a purchase
	So that I can get the product that I want

steps.name: I have added an item to my shopping bag
I proceed to the check out
I enter valid delivery details
I select a payment method
I I confirm the order
I am redirected to the thank you page

elements.name: check02 - Checkout with incorrect delivery details

steps.name: I have added an item to my shopping bag
I click the shopping bag icon
I proceed to check out
I select a payment method
I enter invalid details
I click the pay button
I receive feedback that the purchase details are incorrect

name: Locale selector
description:
As a visitor of the ecommerce website
	I want to be able to change the locale
	So that the site is using my language, country and/or currency

steps.name: I an on a non US/Global/General page
I navigate to the locale selector page
I select US as a country
The US site is shown
I an on the US/Global/General page
I an on the locale selector page
I select a different country than US with a different language
a non-Enlish locale is shown

name: Newsletter
description:
As a visitor of the ecommerce website
	I want to register for the newsletter
	So that I stay up to date on new products and sales

elements.name: news01 - Sign up for the newsletter

steps.name: I can navigate to the newsletter signup from the landing page
I navigate to the newsletter signup
I subscribe to the newsletter
I receive feedback that I have subscribed sucessfully

name: Product detail page
description:
As a visitor of the ecommerce website
	I want to see the details of the product
	So that I know if the product fits my needs

steps.name: I navigate to the site in dutch
I am on a product lister page
I select one of the items
I am on the Product detail page of the selected item
I can see details of the product

name: Product lister page
description:
As a visitor of the ecommerce website
	I want to see an overview of products
	So that I can select a product that fits my needs

elements.name: plp01 - Navigating to a Product lister page

steps.name: I am on the homepage where I can go to a product lister page
I select a Product lister page from the menu
I am on the Product lister page

elements.name: plp02 - Filtering on the Product lister page

steps.name: I am on a Product lister page
I select the filter (...)
I click the button to confirm filtering
the page is filtered to only show (...) products

name: Search
description:
As a visitor of the ecommerce website
	I want to search for products
	So that I can quickly find what I am looking for

elements.name: srch01- Do a valid search with a single keyword

steps.name: I am on the homepage to do a single keyword search
I do a single keyword search for (...)
I see a single keyword search result page with more than zero results

elements.name: srch01- Do a valid search with multiple keyword

steps.name: I am on the homepage to do a search with multiple keywords
I do a multiple keyword search for (... ...)
I see a multiple keyword search result page with more than zero results
I have done a search using a valid search term
I see a certain amount of items
I filter on (...)
The results are filtered to display a smaller amount of items

name: Shopping basket
description:
As a visitor of the ecommerce website
	I want to have a shopping basket
	So that I can see the products and costs of what I want to purchase

steps.name: I have added an item to my shopping bag
I click the shopping bag icon
I land on the shopping bag page
I can see the product in my shopping basket

elements.name: basket02 - Adding a product to basket

steps.name: I am on a product detail page
I select the size/color/amount
I click the add to basket button
the product is added to my shopping basket
